comments: Beal (WAS) extends his arm against Burks' (NYK) shoulder and contact affects his ability to defend.
Burks (NYK) moves laterally in Beal's (WAS) path and initiates contact that affects his driving shot attempt.
Gibson (NYK) moves toward Beal (WAS) and marginal contact occurs during his putback shot attempt.
Matthews (WAS) and Burks (NYK) engage and disengage with one another off ball.
Len (WAS) briefly places his hand to Burks's (NYK) backside and marginal contact occurs during his driving shot attempt.
Barrett's (NYK) arm is already extended against Beal's (WAS) side at the start of his shooting motion and Barrett immediately removes it without applying force.
Gibson (NYK) gathers the loose ball and Westbrook (WAS) dislodges it before incidental contact occurs.
Hachimura (WAS) places his arm to Randle's (NYK) side during his drive and marginal contact occurs.
Len (WAS) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without actively guarding an opponent.
Westbrook (WAS) brings his hand to the side of the ball and not underneath it as he continues his dribble.
Barrett (NYK) moves laterally in Westbrook's (WAS) path and contact affects his SQBR.
Westbrook (WAS) commits a take foul on Burks (NYK).
Len (WAS) establishes himself in a screening position in Burks' (NYK) path and makes marginal contact as they disengage.
Beal (WAS) commits a take foul on Quickley (NYk).
Len (WAS) establishes himself in a screening position in Burks' (NYK) path and gives him a step to avoid contact.
Quickley (NYK) legally contests Matthews' (WAS) jump shot attempt.
Westbrook (WAS) commits a take foul on Burks (NYK).
